{"id":232488078,"title":"溏心蛋🥚簡易版","content":"食材準備\n雞蛋（未冷藏過的）》數顆\n醬油\n味醂\n冰糖or砂糖\n-\n首先，清水洗過雞蛋外殼放置旁邊備用（先不要丟進水煮）\n開火煮水，水滾後，關火靜待2～3分鐘\n就可以輕輕將清洗過的雞蛋放入（建議用撈網或湯匙放雞蛋比較不會破）\n雞蛋都放入水裡後，開中小火煮雞蛋（開始計時大約6:00～7:00，圖片為七分鐘版本）\n邊煮雞蛋時用湯匙在水裡 偶爾順時針或逆時針轉（要統一方向）\n時間到後將雞蛋撈起泡冷水，等到外殼微溫或放涼時即可剝殼\n-\n醬汁部分\n醬油：味醂：開水：糖\n比例為\n1:1:1:0.5\n四種比例一起煮滾後放涼\n即可將撥好殼的蛋放入醬汁\n\n醃漬時間大約12-18小時即可完成✅\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n附上完成圖✨✨（上面是撒蒜味黑胡椒）\nhttps://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vf.jpg","excerpt":"食材準備，雞蛋（未冷藏過的）》數顆，醬油，味醂，冰糖or砂糖，-，首先，清水洗過雞蛋外殼放置旁邊備用（先不要丟進水煮），開火煮水，水滾後，關火靜待2～3分鐘，就可以輕輕將清洗過的雞蛋放入（建議用撈網或","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-12T11:11:23.422Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-12T11:11:23.422Z","commentCount":11,"likeCount":152,"tags":[],"topics":["烹飪","食物"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"逢甲大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":151},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vf.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"5efb7981-5d1d-4585-998d-42fbe97b551c","url":"https://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vfl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vfl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vfl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-12T11:11:23.422Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-12T11:11:23.422Z"},{"id":"5efb7981-5d1d-4585-998d-42fbe97b551c","url":"https://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vf.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/jiCn6vf","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/jiCn6vfl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-12T11:11:23.422Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-12T11:11:23.422Z"}],"postAvatar":""}